Smallville Season 11 #23 (2012)
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  November 23, 2012

Cover by Scott Kolins
Written by Bryan Q. Miller
Art by Axel Gimenez

Superman and Batman enter Mr. Freeze's hideout, but he's not at home. While Freeze is off wreaking havoc downtown, the Prankster greets the heroes wearing his own giant mech suit. As for Lois and Nightwing, they're trying to fight off a horde of deadly assassins.
